</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>Huawei Tag 物件追蹤器登場，其功能與 AirTag 相似</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/07/09/huaweitag/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=huaweitag</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[EMMA]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 09 Jul 2022 07:10:15 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1108365</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Huawei（華為）近日舉行發布會，除了宣佈推出全新的手機 nova 10 系列，亦發布了旗下首個防丟追蹤器產品 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Huawei（華為）近日舉行發布會，除了宣佈推出全新的手機 nova 10 系列，亦發布了旗下首個防丟追蹤器產品 Huawei Tag，售價為＄99 人民幣（約港幣 HK$116）。</p><p>據 Huawei 官方介紹，Huawei Tag 非常輕薄，厚度只有 5.6mm，重 6g，具備 IP67 防塵防水機能和超過一年的續航力。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1108367 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-05-13.04.21-694x410.png" alt="" width="694" height="410" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-05-13.04.21-694x410.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-05-13.04.21-1280x755.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-05-13.04.21-768x453.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-05-13.04.21.png 1532w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1108368 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-05-13.03.51-694x317.png" alt="" width="694" height="317" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-05-13.03.51-694x317.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-05-13.03.51-768x351.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-05-13.03.51.png 1012w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">（圖片來源：Huawei 官方網頁）</p><p>Huawei Tag 支援近距離尋找，有最大 92dB 的響鬧聲能讓用戶循聲辨位。Huawei Tag 亦設有快速提醒模式，若物品丟下超過 15 秒，配對的手機上就會彈出警報。Huawei Tag 的用途與 Apple 推出的 AirTag 相似，主要用作「尋找」其它華為裝置的位置。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1108369 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-05-13.04.40-694x484.png" alt="" width="694" height="484" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-05-13.04.40-694x484.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-05-13.04.40-1280x893.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-05-13.04.40-768x536.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-05-13.04.40-1536x1072.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-05-13.04.40.png 1788w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">（圖片來源：Huawei 官方網頁）</p><p>在私隱方面，Huawei 強調 HUAWEI Tag 的位置資料都會經過加密，若有不屬於本人的 Huawei Tag 長時間跟隨也會觸發警報，用作安全提醒。</p><p>Huawei Tag 單個售價為＄99 人民幣（約＄116 港幣），四件組合裝售價為＄299 人民幣（約＄350 港幣），將於 7 月 30 日率先正式在內地發售。</p><p class="p1"><span class="s1">資料</span><span class="s2">來源：<a href="https://gamingsym.in/one-year-long-battery-life-huawei-tag-anti-lost-wizard-released-for-only-99-yuan/">gamingsym</a></span></p><p class="p1">—</p><p class="p2"><span class="s3">unwire.hk</span> Mewe <span class="s4">專頁：</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span class="s3">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;theme=light&amp;color=white&amp;controls=0&amp;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player" a